# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Field gun platoons crew heavy LB-X autocannons with dual-ammunition capability, able to fire armor-piercing slugs against vehicles or cluster rounds that scatter across a wide area against soft targets. The heavier LB-X variants deliver punishing firepower in either mode, though the weapon system demands significant logistics support and trained crews who can select the right ammunition type under pressure.</p>
</overview>

